data.description: Welcome to this beautiful two story home, 5 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms in Schertz offering $5,000 in seller concessions! Enough space for the whole family & more! Huge master suite with large walk in closet. Two living areas perfect for family area and a game room or media room! Not to mention a flex room that can be used as an office, formal dining or however you want! The spacious back yard has enough privacy, a large patio area covered by a pergola. This home is close to JBSA-Randolph & JBSA-Fort Sam Houston, shopping centers & Schertz/Cibolo School District. So if you're looking to upgrade to a larger home, this is the one for y'all!
